pick up knife from counter
turn around, turn right to the counter
slice the potato on the counter
turn around, turn left to the fridge
open door, place knife on to the shelf, close door

high_descs: Turn to your right and go across the kitchen to the counter top between the stove and the refrigerator.
Pick up the knife to the right of the apple on the counter top.
Turn around and walk across the kitchen, then turn to the counter top on your right, just before the microwave.
Cut the potato in front of the egg, on the counter, into slices.
Turn around and go to the end of the counter, then turn to your left and go to the refrigerator.
Place the knife on the top shelf of the refrigerator, in front of the loaf of bread.
Turn around and go back to the end of the counter, turn right and go to the counter across from you where the potato  is.
Pick up one of the potato slices.
Turn around and go to the end of the counter, then turn to your left and go to the refrigerator.
Place the tomato slice on the top shelf of the refrigerator, to the right of the head of lettuce, wait a moment for the potato slice to chill, then remove the potato slice from the refrigerator.
Move over to your right, to the garbage bin on the floor to the right of the refrigerator.
Put the potato slice in the garbage bin on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in the refrigerator and a cold potato slice in the garbage.

high_descs: Turn around to walk to the counter by the toaster.
Pick up the knife.
Turn left to walk back to the counter to the left of the sink.
Slice the potato on the counter with the knife.
Turn right to walk to the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Turn left to walk to the counter above the dishwasher.
Pick up a slice of potato from the counter.
Make a right and walk to the fridge.
Chill the potato slice in the fridge, removing it afterwards.
Make a right to reach the trash can next to the fridge.
Put the potato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Chill a potato slice in the fridge to throw away in the trash can.
